Setting up autostart...
Installation complete!

Next steps:
1. Restart GNOME Shell (Alt+F2, r, Enter) or log out/in
2. You should see a microphone icon in the top panel
3. Start the daemon: whisper-aloud --daemon
4. Click the icon to control recording

To uninstall:
  gnome-extensions disable whisperaloud@fede
  rm -rf /home/fede/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions/whisperaloud@fede
  rm /home/fede/.config/autostart/whisperaloud-daemon.desktop
